Terrence Evans https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Terrence_Evans 0 Terrence Howard Evans (June 21, 1934 – August 7, 2015) was an American-born Welsh film and stage actor. His parents met on the RMS Berengaria while coming to America from Wales in 1929. Terrence_Howard_Evans ( June_21_,_1934 – August_7_,_2015 ) was an_American-born_Welsh_film_and_stage_actor .
